Thence leaving said westerly right of way and said existing City of Columbus Corporation Line Ordinance# 1337-2016, crossing said Hillard & Rome Road (R/W varies) along existing City of Columbus Corporation Line Ordinance# 2530-2020 as recorded in Instrument Number 202102180031222, Easterly, approximately 116 feet to a point in the westerly right of way of Rome & Hilliard Road East (R/W varies); 
